posts.post_content:
Fairly new member/poster and have only been collecting T206 cards for a few months. In truth, this set and these cards brought me back to collecting and it has been really enjoyable. I’ve bought some really cool cards and have had a great experience so far, can’t say enough about this site and the members. That truth/fluff aside, my two projects so far are collecting Cubs and the Elite 11/12 cards. I’ve got some work to do on the latter so would be grateful if anyone has any to offer, will consider all offers!

Thank you

Andy
